'''Saam-zi-gang''' heh [[Zung-kok]] geh tsen-thung gaau sai-man-zai geh si. Yi-tsen  heung hok-haau ngit-ding fui gaau gaai si. Gaai si nui-yung yu Zung-kok 5000 nen [[Vùn-fa|wun-fa]], lak-si, tset-hok, then-wun-thi-li, ngin-lun-yi-li, chung haau zit-yi dang-dang. Gam yu thoi-biu Saam-zi-gang geh nui-yung haau fung-fu. Li chung si yu baau-kut choh ngin ge daau-li.

